body:
Welcome to the GitHub Pages homepage for the lulzBot project, a project aiming to create a relatively simple bot for dAmn (deviantART's Message Network) in C# that will boast a wide array of features while still maintaining ease of use.


The project is under development by [DivinityArcane](http://divinityarcane.deviantart.com/?rnrd=31226) and [OrrinFox](http://orrinfox.deviantart.com/?rnrd=35930).
name: lulzBot
